title: DreadOut-CODEX
description:
CODEX PRESENTS:


                               DreadOut Act I

  Release Date :  5/2014                         Protection : Steam
  Discs        :  1                              Genre      : Adventure


DreadOut is a third person supernatural horror game where you play as Linda,
a high school student trapped in an old abandoned town. Equipped with her
trusty smart-phone, she will battle against terrifying encounters and solve
mysterious puzzles which will ultimately determine her fate.
Help her overcome the challenges that will stand before her. Survive the
Dread!


 - Extract
 - Burn or mount the .iso
 - Run setup.exe and install
 - Copy crack from CODEX folder to your installdir
 - Play

 Block game exe in your firewall to prevent the game from trying to go
 online ..
